352static bool IsEncounterFinished(Unit* who)
353{
354 InstanceScript* instance = who->GetInstanceScript();
355
356 Creature* mkii = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*who, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_LEVIATHAN_MK_II));
357 Creature* vx001 = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*who, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_VX_001));
358 Creature* aerial = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*who, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_AERIAL_COMMAND_UNIT));
359 if (!mkii || !vx001 || !aerial)
360 return false;
361
362 if (mkii->GetStandState() == UNIT_STAND_STATE_DEAD &&
363 vx001->GetStandState() == UNIT_STAND_STATE_DEAD &&
364 aerial->GetStandState() == UNIT_STAND_STATE_DEAD)
365 {
366 who->Kill(mkii);
367 who->Kill(vx001);
368 who->Kill(aerial);
369 mkii->DespawnOrUnsummon(120000);
370 vx001->DespawnOrUnsummon(120000);
371 aerial->DespawnOrUnsummon(120000);
372 if (Creature* mimiron = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*who, instance->GetGuidData(BOSS_MIMIRON)))
373 mimiron->AI()->JustDied(who);
374 return true;
375 }
376 return false;
377}
378
379class boss_mimiron : public CreatureScript
380{
381 public:
382 boss_mimiron() : CreatureScript("boss_mimiron") { }
383
384 struct boss_mimironAI : public BossAI
385 {
386 boss_mimironAI(Creature* creature) : BossAI(creature, BOSS_MIMIRON)
387 {
388 me->SetReactState(REACT_PASSIVE);
389 _fireFighter = false;
390 }
391
392 void DoAction(int32 action) override
393 {
394 switch (action)
395 {
396 case DO_ACTIVATE_VX001:
397 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_1, 1000);
398 break;
399 case DO_ACTIVATE_AERIAL:
400 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_AERIAL_ACTIVATION_1, 5000);
401 break;
402 case DO_ACTIVATE_V0L7R0N_1:
403 Talk(SAY_AERIAL_DEATH);
404 if (Creature* mkii = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_LEVIATHAN_MK_II)))
405 mkii->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(WP_MKII_P4_POS_1, VehicleRelocation[WP_MKII_P4_POS_1]);
406 break;
407 case DO_ACTIVATE_V0L7R0N_2:
408 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VOL7RON_ACTIVATION_1, 1000);
409 break;
410 case DO_ACTIVATE_HARD_MODE:
411 _fireFighter = true;
412 DoZoneInCombat(me);
413 break;
414 default:
415 break;
416 }
417 }
418
419 void EnterCombat(Unit* /*who*/) override
420 {
421 if (!me->GetVehicleBase())
422 return;
423
424 _EnterCombat();
425 me->SetFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE);
426 me->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_WELD);
427 DoCast(me->GetVehicleBase(), SPELL_SEAT_6);
428
429 if (GameObject* button = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_BUTTON)))
430 button->SetFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
431
432 if (_fireFighter)
433 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_FLAMES, 3000);
434 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_1, 1500);
435 }
436
437 void JustDied(Unit* /*who*/) override
438 {
439 instance->SetBossState(BOSS_MIMIRON, DONE);
440 events.Reset();
441 me->CombatStop(true);
442 me->SetDisableGravity(false);
443 DoCast(me, SPELL_SLEEP_VISUAL_1);
444 DoCastAOE(SPELL_DESPAWN_ASSAULT_BOTS);
445 me->ExitVehicle();
446 // ExitVehicle() offset position is not implemented, so we make up for that with MoveJump()...
447 me->GetMotionMaster()->MoveJump(me->GetPositionX() + (10.f * std::cos(me->GetOrientation())), me->GetPositionY() + (10.f * std::sin(me->GetOrientation())), me->GetPositionZ(), 10.f, 5.f);
448 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_OUTTRO_1, 7000);
449 }
450
451 void Reset() override
452 {
453 if (instance->GetBossState(BOSS_MIMIRON) == DONE) // Mimiron will attempt to reset because he is not dead and will be set to friendly before despawning.
454 return;
455
456 _Reset();
457 me->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE);
458
459 if (GameObject* elevator = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_ELEVATOR)))
460 elevator->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE);
461
462 if (_fireFighter)
463 if (Creature* computer = ObjectAccessor::GetCreature(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_COMPUTER)))
464 computer->AI()->DoAction(DO_DEACTIVATE_COMPUTER);
465
466 if (GameObject* button = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_BUTTON)))
467 {
468 button->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
469 button->RemoveFlag(GAMEOBJECT_FLAGS, GO_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
470 }
471
472 _fireFighter = false;
473 DoCast(me, SPELL_WELD);
474
475 if (Unit* mkii = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_LEVIATHAN_MK_II)))
476 DoCast(mkii, SPELL_SEAT_3);
477 }
478
479 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
480 {
481 if ((!UpdateVictim() || !CheckInRoom()) && instance->GetBossState(BOSS_MIMIRON) != DONE)
482 return;
483
484 events.Update(diff);
485
486 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
487 return;
488
489 while (uint32 eventId = events.ExecuteEvent())
490 {
491 switch (eventId)
492 {
493 case EVENT_SUMMON_FLAMES:
494 if (Unit* worldtrigger = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_WORLD_TRIGGER)))
495 worldtrigger->CastCustomSpell(SPELL_SCRIPT_EFFECT_SUMMON_FLAMES_INITIAL, SPELLVALUE_MAX_TARGETS, 3, NULL, true, NULL, NULL, me->GetGUID());
496 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SUMMON_FLAMES, 28000);
497 break;
498 case EVENT_INTRO_1:
499 Talk(_fireFighter ? SAY_HARDMODE_ON : SAY_MKII_ACTIVATE);
500 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_2, 5000);
501 break;
502 case EVENT_INTRO_2:
503 if (Unit* mkii = me->GetVehicleBase())
504 {
505 DoCast(mkii, SPELL_SEAT_7);
506 mkii->RemoveAurasDueToSpell(SPELL_FREEZE_ANIM);
507 mkii->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE | UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
508 }
509 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_INTRO_3, 2000);
510 break;
511 case EVENT_INTRO_3:
512 if (Creature* mkii = me->GetVehicleCreatureBase())
513 mkii->AI()->DoAction(_fireFighter ? DO_HARDMODE_MKII : DO_START_MKII);
514 break;
515 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_1:
516 if (Unit* mkii = me->GetVehicleBase())
517 mkii->SetFacingTo(3.686f); // fix magic number
518 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_2, 1000);
519 break;
520 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_2:
521 if (Unit* mkii = me->GetVehicleBase())
522 DoCast(mkii, SPELL_SEAT_6);
523 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_3, 1000);
524 break;
525 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_3:
526 Talk(SAY_MKII_DEATH);
527 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_4, 5000);
528 break;
529 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_4:
530 if (GameObject* elevator = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_ELEVATOR)))
531 elevator->SetGoState(GO_STATE_READY);
532 if (Unit* worldtrigger = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_WORLD_TRIGGER)))
533 worldtrigger->CastSpell(worldtrigger, SPELL_ELEVATOR_KNOCKBACK);
534 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_5, 6000);
535 break;
536 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_5:
537 if (GameObject* elevator = ObjectAccessor::GetGameObject(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_MIMIRON_ELEVATOR)))
538 elevator->SetGoState(GO_STATE_ACTIVE_ALTERNATIVE);
539 if (Creature* vx001 = me->SummonCreature(NPC_VX_001, VX001SummonPos, TEMPSUMMON_CORPSE_TIMED_DESPAWN, 120000))
540 vx001->CastSpell(vx001, SPELL_FREEZE_ANIM);
541 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_6, 19000);
542 break;
543 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_6:
544 if (Unit* vx001 = ObjectAccessor::GetUnit(*me, instance->GetGuidData(DATA_VX_001)))
545 DoCast(vx001, SPELL_SEAT_1);
546 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_7, 3500);
547 break;
548 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_7:
549 Talk(SAY_VX001_ACTIVATE);
550 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_8, 4000);
551 break;
552 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_8:
553 if (Unit* vx001 = me->GetVehicleBase())
554 DoCast(vx001, SPELL_SEAT_2);
555 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_9, 3000);
556 break;
557 case EVENT_VX001_ACTIVATION_9:
558 if (Creature* vx001 = me->GetVehicleCreatureBase())
559 vx001->AI()->DoAction(_fireFighter ? DO_HARDMODE_VX001 : DO_START_VX001);
560 break;
561 case EVENT_AERIAL_ACTIVATION_1:
562 if (Unit* mkii = me->GetVehicleBase())
563 DoCast(mkii, SPELL_SEAT_5);
564 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_AERIAL_ACTIVATION_2, 2500);
565 break;
566 case EVENT_AERIAL_ACTIVATION_2:
567 Talk(SAY_VX001_DEATH);
568 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_AERIAL_ACTIVATION_3, 5000);
569 break;

689 void DamageTaken(Unit* who, uint32 &damage) override

710 {
711 me->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_DEAD);
712
713 if (IsEncounterFinished(who))
714 return;
715
716 me->CastStop();
717 DoCast(me, SPELL_SELF_REPAIR);
718 }
719 events.Reset();
720 }

731 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_MK, 60000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);

736
737 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_NAPALM_SHELL, 3000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);
738 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PLASMA_BLAST, 15000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);
739 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PROXIMITY_MINE, 5000);
740 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOCK_BLAST, 18000);
741 break;
742 case DO_ASSEMBLED_COMBAT:
743 me->SetStandState(UNIT_STAND_STATE_STAND);
744 me->RemoveFlag(UNIT_FIELD_FLAGS, UNIT_FLAG_NON_ATTACKABLE | UNIT_FLAG_NOT_SELECTABLE);
745 me->SetReactState(REACT_AGGRESSIVE);
746
747 events.SetPhase(PHASE_VOL7RON);
748 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_PROXIMITY_MINE, 15000);
749 events.ScheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOCK_BLAST, 45000);
750 break;

847 void UpdateAI(uint32 diff) override
848 {
849 if (!UpdateVictim() || !CheckInRoom())
850 return;
851
852 events.Update(diff);
853
854 if (me->HasUnitState(UNIT_STATE_CASTING))
855 return;
856
857 while (uint32 eventId = events.ExecuteEvent())
858 {
859 switch (eventId)
860 {
861 case EVENT_PROXIMITY_MINE:
862 DoCastAOE(SPELL_PROXIMITY_MINES);
863 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_PROXIMITY_MINE, 35000);
864 break;
865 case EVENT_PLASMA_BLAST:
866 DoCastVictim(SPELL_SCRIPT_EFFECT_PLASMA_BLAST);
867 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_PLASMA_BLAST, urand(30000, 45000), 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);
868
869 if (events.GetTimeUntilEvent(EVENT_NAPALM_SHELL) < 9000)
870 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_NAPALM_SHELL, 9000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II); // The actual spell is cast by the turret, we should not let it interrupt itself.
871 break;
872 case EVENT_SHOCK_BLAST:
873 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SHOCK_BLAST);
874 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SHOCK_BLAST, urand(34000, 36000));
875 break;
876 case EVENT_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_MK:
877 DoCastAOE(SPELL_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_MK);
878 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_MK, 60000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);
879 break;
880 case EVENT_NAPALM_SHELL:
881 DoCastAOE(SPELL_FORCE_CAST_NAPALM_SHELL);
882 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_NAPALM_SHELL, urand(6000, 15000), 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II);
883
884 if (events.GetTimeUntilEvent(EVENT_PLASMA_BLAST) < 2000)
885 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_PLASMA_BLAST, 2000, 0, PHASE_LEVIATHAN_MK_II); // The actual spell is cast by the turret, we should not let it interrupt itself.
886 break;
887 case EVENT_MOVE_POINT_2:
888 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(WP_MKII_P4_POS_2, VehicleRelocation[WP_MKII_P4_POS_2]);
889 break;
890 case EVENT_MOVE_POINT_3:
891 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(WP_MKII_P4_POS_3, VehicleRelocation[WP_MKII_P4_POS_3]);
892 break;
893 case EVENT_MOVE_POINT_5:
894 me->GetMotionMaster()->MovePoint(WP_MKII_P4_POS_5, VehicleRelocation[WP_MKII_P4_POS_5]);
895 break;
896 default:
897 break;
898 }
899 }
900 DoMeleeAttackIfReady();
901 }

906 bool _setupBomb;

1038 me->SetFacingToObject(channelTarget);

1057 for (int8 seat = ROCKET_SEAT_LEFT; seat <= ROCKET_SEAT_RIGHT; ++seat)

1062 if (Unit* target = SelectTarget(SELECT_TARGET_RANDOM, 0, 120, true))
1063 DoCast(target, RAND(SPELL_HAND_PULSE_LEFT, SPELL_HAND_PULSE_RIGHT));
1064 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_HAND_PULSE, urand(1500, 3000), 0, PHASE_VOL7RON);
1065 break;
1066 case EVENT_FROST_BOMB:
1067 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SCRIPT_EFFECT_FROST_BOMB);
1068 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_FROST_BOMB, 45000);
1069 break;
1070 case EVENT_SPINNING_UP:
1071 DoCastAOE(SPELL_SPINNING_UP);
1072 events.DelayEvents(14000);
1073 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_SPINNING_UP, urand(55000, 65000));
1074 break;
1075 case EVENT_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_VX:
1076 DoCastAOE(SPELL_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_VX);
1077 events.RescheduleEvent(EVENT_FLAME_SUPPRESSANT_VX, urand(10000, 12000), 0, PHASE_VX_001);
1078 break;
1079 default:
1080 break;
1081 }
1082 }

2528// 64562 - Summon Flames Spread Trigger
2529class spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread : public SpellScriptLoader
2530{
2531 public:
2532 spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread() : SpellScriptLoader("spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread") { }

2535 {
2536 PrepareSpellScript(spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread_SpellScript);
2537
2538 void FilterTargets(std::list<WorldObject*>& targets)
2539 {
2540 if (targets.empty())
2541 return;
2542
2543 // Flames must chase the closest player
2544 WorldObject* target = targets.front();
2545
2546 for (std::list<WorldObject*>::const_iterator iter = targets.begin(); iter != targets.end(); ++iter)
2547 if (GetCaster()->GetDistance2d(*iter) < GetCaster()->GetDistance2d(target))
2548 target = *iter;
2549
2550 targets.clear();
2551 targets.push_back(target);
2552 }
2553
2554 void OnHit(SpellEffIndex /*effIndex*/)
2555 {
2556 GetCaster()->SetInFront(GetHitUnit());
2557 }
2558
2559 void Register() override
2560 {
2561 OnObjectAreaTargetSelect += SpellObjectAreaTargetSelectFn(spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread_SpellScript::FilterTargets, EFFECT_0, TARGET_UNIT_SRC_AREA_ENEMY);
2562 OnEffectHitTarget += SpellEffectFn(spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread_SpellScript::OnHit, EFFECT_0, SPELL_EFFECT_APPLY_AURA);
2563 }
2564 };

2566 SpellScript* GetSpellScript() const override

2568 return new spell_mimiron_summon_flames_spread_SpellScript();
